Package com.wx.util.representables.string

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BooleanRepr
    Allows to cast a boolean into String and vice-versa.
    CharRepr
    Casts a String into char and vice-versa.
    DirectoryRepr
    Cast a file from a string (and vice-versa) ensuring that the file is a directory and (possibly) automatically creates the directory.
    DoubleRepr  
    EncodedBytesRepr
    Easily cast from bytes to hexadecimal String and vice-versa.
    EncryptedRepr
    Easily cast from bytes to a string representation of their encrypted value.
    EnumCaster<E extends java.lang.Enum<E>>
    Allows to cast enum values to string by using their name
    EnumCasterLC<E extends java.lang.Enum<E>>
    Similar to the EnumCaster but enforces the use of lower case in the String representation.
    FileRepr
    Cast from a file to string and vice versa.
    FloatRepr  
    IntRepr  
    ListRepr<E>  
    LongRepr  
    MapRepr<K,V>  
    NullSafeCaster<InType,OutType>
    This is class wraps another caster ensuring that no null value is ever passed to the sub caster (but directly returns null instead).
    PairRepr<E,F>  
    SetRepr<E>  
    StringRepr
